Package: ecfr.gov
Title: Electronic Code of Federal Regulations (eCFR) API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the eCFR API. Browse CFR titles,
    search full text, view title structure, and track regulatory changes.
    Includes LLM context injection via ecfr_context().
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
